<div class="m-form-row__help" data-module="m-form-row__help">
<p class="m-form-row__explanatory-text">A regular smoker smokes 10 or more cigarettes a day, or a minimum of 3oz rolling tobacco, for the last 10 years.</p>
<p class="m-form-row__explanatory-text">If you smoke less than this, it may still have an impact on your life expectancy.</p>
